---
// src/components/Features.astro
---
<section class="features">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="features-grid">
      <article class="feature-card">
        <h3 class="feature-title">Engineered for Excellence</h3>
        <p>
          Every batch is crafted with military precision. No shortcuts, no compromises. Just the relentless pursuit of perfection in every drop, engineered for those who demand the absolute best.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="feature-card">
        <h3 class="feature-title">Essential Provision</h3>
        <p>
          Built for functionality over flash. This isn't a decoration for your shelf—it's a tool for adventurers, makers, and those who value substance over style. Purpose-built for real experiences.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="feature-card">
        <h3 class="feature-title">Inspired by Resilience</h3>
        <p>
          Born from the legacy of the jerry can—a symbol of resourcefulness and durability. We carry that same spirit of resilience into every bottle, honoring those who came before.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features {
    background-color: var(--parchment);
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .feature-card {
    border: 2px solid rgba(42, 47, 29, 0.2);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background-color: #fff;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .feature-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--deep-green);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--olive-drab);
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    display: inline-block;
    min-height: 70px;
  }
  .feature-card p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--dark-olive);
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .feature-title {
        min-height: auto;
    }
  }
</style>